 <h2>Immersion in<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;other worlds...</h2>
 <p class="intro1">Author, environmentalist, film-maker, international motivational speaker.</p>
 <p class="intro2">Benedict Allen became established as one of the world's leading modern-day explorers through expeditions famously achieved not with a phone, <abbr title="Global Positioning System">GPS</abbr> or "backup," but by preparation alone with remote indigenous communities. Dispensing with a film crew, he went on to pioneer the authentic recording of adventurous journeys for TV.</p>
