<h2>Upcoming events</h2>

<p style="margin-bottom:0.5em;">26th February 2020:</p>

<h3 style="font-size:1.65em; line-height:1em;">Presenting the Stanford Dolman Travel Book of the Year award.</h3>

<img src="../images/Stanford_Dolman_Book_award.jpg" class="imgborder" style="width:24em; margin-top:0.3em;">
<p style="line-height: 1.2em;">The Edward Stanford Travel Writing Awards ceremony on 26th February 2020 will be held at The London Transport Museum, in Central London. There will be a Cocktail Reception & Global Food Feast at 7:00pm, followed by the Awards Ceremony. The awards will be hosted by Julia Bradbury.<br>&nbsp;</p>

<p style="line-height: 1.2em;">Venue: London Transport Museum, Covent Garden Piazza, London, WC2E 7BB.<br>
Starts 7:00pm. Dress Code: Smart Casual.</p>

